Instalation:
    - Install mysql server on your laptop from mysql website
    - mysql -u root -p "PASSWORD" -h 127.0.0.1 (login to mysql client)
    - In mysql prompts into mysql command prompt: 
        - create databases Blackjack; (this creates the database on your local computer)
        - quit; (exits out of mysql client)
    - In normal terminal run:
        - mysql -u root -p "PASSWORD" -h 127.0.0.1 Blackjack < blackjack.sql

